description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News - Goblins, Bigfoot & Ghosts of War Edition

Dave & Tim peel back the veneer of safety we all feel nestled in our homes to discuss Goblin Attacks, a Superpowered Bigfoot, Loretta Lynn vs The Spirit World and Dave rants while Tim checks Dave's ego at the door...all that plus new Theater of the Mind and listeners tales of the Supernatural.

Watch the Season 2 Finale of Holzer Files starring Darkness Dave this Saturday.
